{"tid":1660892,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【颱風追擊】1920號熱帶氣旋 浣熊 NEOGURI（21W）","createTime":"2019-10-17T19:38:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-19T13:56:37.000Z","uid":38255,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"65cec526beb5d2bb71f7801cfff60e09e2dad26b","tid":1660892,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T19:38:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://imgur.com/Pskei0w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FPskei0w.png&h=13bd482a&s={SIZE}\" /><strong><span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins>颱風追擊：熱帶氣旋 浣熊</ins></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1920號熱帶氣旋 浣熊 NEOGURI（21W）</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">來源：南韓<br />\n意義：狗浣熊，生性靈巧，身體細小，呈灰啡色，面上有黑色斑紋，有粗的毛尾</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zytwd8L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fzytwd8L.jpg&h=930547f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【註】 發出颱風追擊帖，表示有熱帶氣旋在南海或西北太平洋一帶形成。　<br />\n為使大家有一個良好舒適的瀏覽環境，請不要張貼未經證實的風暴消息、使用簡體中文貼文、提及力場或洗版，謝謝合作。　<br />\n請勿直接張貼會自動更新的氣象圖片，請把圖片上傳至儲存空間後再轉貼在帖文上。謝謝。　<br />\n <br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">請關注<span style=\"color: red;\">氣象巴打&bull;高登氣象台</span>最新動態<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgur.com/z4brcbr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2Fz4brcbr.png&h=d512611e&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"http://imgur.com/2v9xh70.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2F2v9xh70.png&h=7ef830e1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://imgur.com/gnzQsWS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FgnzQsWS.png&h=54316817&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://imgur.com/7sNQ3N2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2F7sNQ3N2.png&h=15a63bfa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</span></em><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">連登圖片似乎無法取消截取緩存，有機會顯示出較舊時期的圖片，若以下圖片並非最新資訊，可選擇「在瀏覽器中開啟」獲取最新圖片。</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏</span> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\"><ins>◤熱帶氣旋路徑圖</ins></span></span> <br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/wxinfo/currwx/nwp_1928.png\" /> <br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/wxinfo/currwx/tc_1928.png\" /> <br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/wxinfo/currwx/zoom_1928.png\" /> <br />\n▲香港天文台(HKO) <br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://www.jma.go.jp/jp/typh/images/zooml/1920-00.png\" /> <img data-no-cache src=\"http://www.jma.go.jp/jp/typh/images/zoom5l/1920-00.png\" /> <br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://www.jma.go.jp/jp/typh/images/zoom24l/1920-00.png\" /> <br />\n▲ 日本氣象廳 (JMA) <br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"https://pzal.ndbc.noaa.gov/collab/jtwc/products/wp2119.gif\" /> <img data-no-cache src=\"http://www.tropicalstormrisk.com/tracker/dynamic/images/201921W.png\" /> <br />\n▲ 聯合颱風警報中心 (JTWC) <br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://typhoon2000.ph/multi/data/NEOGURI.PNG\" /><br />\n▲各機構綜合預測</strong>"},{"pid":"de6bf05a07d8cf52bf3219e3073b922974cad1bb","tid":1660892,"uid":213446,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T19:40:07.000Z","msg":"今日凌晨冇琴日凌晨咁涼"},{"pid":"c5a8f7d865da9a8f9164c2b0ef45f239b2239d8b","tid":1660892,"uid":38255,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T19:43:08.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\"><ins>◤颱風追擊必備資訊</ins></span></span><br />\n<br />\n◆ 香港天文台 (HKO)：<a href=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/informtc/tcSmap_uc.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hko.gov.hk%2Finformtc%2FtcSmap_uc.htm&d=vw1niP5YtVVR3vfDaqqaAUVeFFKYYtZMgzuY3n553xQ%3D&h=f64084a8\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hko.gov.hk/informtc/tcSmap_uc.htm</a><br />\n◆ 日本氣象廳 (JMA)：<a 